main event: A UFO sighting occurred on 7 May 1966, where a round object with a bright light was observed for 35 seconds before it accelerated and vanished.
interesting points: The object hovered briefly before accelerating and disappearing from view,The sighting was documented in Project Blue Book, The observer reported that lights in their house went off and on during the sighting, The object was described as almost circular and as large as a house, No other reports were filed regarding this sighting by the police.
sighted object: a round object with a bright light
witness description: 19-year-old male who observed the object from his home
